[normal]1.3 Creative Skillset leads and chairs the Creative Industries Council Skills Group. The Creative Industries Council (CIC) is a forum for i
[normal]ndustries and Governmen
[normal]t to engage in a joined up way 
[normal]to boosting the growth and
[normal] competitiveness of the creative industries.
