[normal]f
[normal]o
[normal]r
[normal] people to create
[normal] content that is representative of all the UK communities and can entertain, educate and inspire. This type of content can
[normal] only
[normal] be produced by people who are 
[normal]skilled and have their
[normal] talent, professional abilities and business acumen
[normal] nurtured
[normal]. 
[normal]The
[normal] 
[normal]BBC 
[normal]should continue to be involved 
[normal]at every level of the
[normal] education and skills system
[normal] 
[normal]so 
