[normal]can 
[normal]be achieved. 
[normal] 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]3
[normal].3 
[normal]T
[normal]he development of talent and skills for the creative media industries 
[normal]should become one of the new Pu
[normal]blic Purposes of the BBC 
[normal]in its future Charter and Framework Agreement. This purpose should come with the expectation that the BBC will continue to work in partnership with industry-wide organisations. 
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]3
[normal].4 T
[normal]he 
[normal]BBC 
[normal]also
[normal] 
[normal]set
[normal]s
[normal] an example 
[normal](and a trend) 
