[normal] 
[normal]The industry will welcome 
[normal]consistency of how 
[normal]the BBC
[normal]’s
[normal] 
[normal]vision will be supported by its resource and inv
[normal]estment in the futu
[normal]re; how the BBC will continue its role in the 
[normal]efforts to build sustaina
[normal]ble industry out-of-London and across the 
[normal]UK Nations, as well as be a key player in addressing issues of fair access, equality of opportunity and representation of the industry-wide wor
[normal]kforce. 
